text: Hello Uncle when u push cart out please stand on the opposite side pull the cart out and not in front of the cart when blocking your view how u expect to see your front view ? When reaching the corridor stop look left and right before pushing out. What if it happens to be a small kid running past ? You can't expect the passage way to be always clear . Things are not always in our favour . Don't make noise . When we are working Open eyes big n see be wary of our surroundings sometimes.
I live in this HDB block, I get most of my snacks and drinks here...
